ll-shows/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wider Than Pictures</a>系列音乐会中演出。他们还将出现在爱丁堡的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boygenius-fred-again-primal-scream-to-headline-scotlands-connect-festival-2023-3407807">Connect Festival 音乐节</a>和多塞特郡的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/end-of-the-road-festival-adds-more-acts-to-2023-line-up-3419003">End of the Road Festival</a>音乐节上。</p><p>此外，未来群岛将于下周在曼彻斯特支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 的高飞鸟乐队 (High Flying Birds)</a> ，并将在米德尔斯堡、剑桥、诺维奇和伍尔弗汉普顿举办自己的头条演出。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/future-islands-tickets/artist/47863?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=TUeRTURCWxyNT8CXSVXWIUg%3AUkF33kz%3AiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/future-islands-as-long-as-you-are-review-2771079">《As Long As You Are》的四星评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>将这张专辑描述为“也许是未来群岛的一个意想不到的手刹转变”。</p><p>它补充道：“它可能不像它的前身那样热门，但它本身就是一张令人耳目一新的唱片，并且引发了很多存在主义的困境。”</p></div></div><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/future-islands-return-with-heart-wrenching-ballad-deep-in-the-night-3483287">未来群岛回归后，带着令人心碎的民谣“Deep In The Night”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 “Old School RuneScape”帐户被劫持并将其转移给黑客https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-to-transfer-them-to-hackers-3483282?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=old-school-runescape-帐户被劫持并将其转移给黑客Imogen DonovanTue, 15 Aug 2023 14:02:44 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3483282 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Jagex 正在联系受影响的人</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-to-transfer-them-to-hackers-3483282">“Old School RuneScape”帐户被劫持并转移给黑客的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/old-school-runescape"><em>Old School RuneScape</em></a>帐户已被不良行为者劫持，使他们能够将受害者的帐户附加到黑客的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a>帐户。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/how-farming-in-old-school-runescape-fixed-my-morning-misery-3380318">“Old School RuneScape”中的农业如何解决我早上的痛苦</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/jagex">Jagex</a>在<em>Old School RuneScape</em>网站上的一篇<a href="https://secure.runescape.com/m=news/regarding-character-linking-concerns?oldschool=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新闻文章</a>中宣布：“我们意识到一个问题，该问题允许玩家的角色通过社交媒体上共享的恶意链接通过 Steam 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/amazon">Amazon</a>帐户链接成为目标。”</p><p>这些链接能够允许从另一个 Steam 帐户访问受害者的<em>Old School RuneScape</em>帐户，只要受害者在点击链接时登录了他们的<em>RuneScape</em>帐户。如果他们没有登录，系统会要求他们登录，并且不会弹出窗口来确保玩家不会将帐户交给未知的演员。</p><p>此外，有报道称这<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/2007scape/comments/15qp6w8/psa_there_seems_to_be_an_exploit_with_the_jagex/">也影响了 Jagex 帐户</a>，尽管开发者表示该漏洞与这些帐户无关。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473756" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473756" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473756" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473756" class="wp-caption-text"> “老派 RuneScape” 图片来源：Jagex</figcaption></figure><p> Jagex 继续说道：“虽然我们没有任何证据表明这对大量玩家产生了影响，但团队目前正在努力找出受此影响的任何帐户。”</p><p> “我们打算直接与个人联系，这意味着您不需要联系我们。我们还在探索可用的选项来退回因此而丢失的任何物品。”</p><p>开发人员决定关闭<em>Old School RuneScape</em>帐户与外部服务 Steam 和 Amazon 的链接功能，直到找到安全漏洞的解决方案。该团队总结道：“我们非常认真地对待这个问题，并希望尽快与您分享更多信息。”</p><p>在其他地方，玩家们也开始尝试<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/old-school-runescape-quest-desert-treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-3473743"><em>《沙漠宝藏 2 - 堕落帝国》</em></a> ，这是游戏中最受喜爱的任务线之一的续作。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-to-transfer-them-to-hackers-3483282">“Old School RuneScape”帐户被劫持并转移给黑客的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
